<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> — Vivid Views</title>
  <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#00d4ff">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root { --bg: #050d1a; --cyan: #00d4ff; --purple: #7c3aed; --gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #7c3aed); --text: #f0f6ff; --text-secondary: #64748b; --card-bg: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); --card-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    body::before { content: ''; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,212,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,212,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 50px 50px; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; }
    .welcome-container { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 700px; width: 100%; padding: 24px; text-align: center; }
    .welcome-title { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; background: var(--gradient); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .welcome-sub { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .step { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--card-border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px 20px; transition: all 0.3s; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .step::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--gradient); }
    .step:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.3); box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,212,255,0.1); }
    .step-icon { font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .step-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .step-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; }
    .step-num { position: absolute; top: 12px; right: 16px; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; color: rgba(0,212,255,0.06); }
    .btn-start { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 14px 40px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; background: var(--gradient); color: #fff; border: none; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; font-family: inherit; box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,212,255,0.2); }
    .btn-start:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(0,212,255,0.3); }
    @keyframes fadeInUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    .step:nth-child(1) { animation: fadeInUp 0.5s 0.1s both; }
    .step:nth-child(2) { animation: fadeInUp 0.5s 0.3s both; }
    .step:nth-child(3) { animation: fadeInUp 0.5s 0.5s both; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .welcome-title { font-size: 28px; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="welcome-container">
    <h1 class="welcome-title">Welcome to Your Portal, <%= user.companyName %>! 👋</h1>
    <p class="welcome-sub">Here's a quick overview of what you can do.</p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-num">1</span>
        <div class="step-icon">📋</div>
        <div class="step-title">Submit Requests</div>
        <div class="step-desc">Create service requests for any of your sites — fast, simple, and tracked.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-num">2</span>
        <div class="step-icon">📊</div>
        <div class="step-title">Track Progress</div>
        <div class="step-desc">Watch your requests move from submitted to complete in real time.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-num">3</span>
        <div class="step-icon">💬</div>
        <div class="step-title">Communicate</div>
        <div class="step-desc">Comment on requests and get updates directly in the portal.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <form method="POST" action="/portal/welcome/complete">
      <button type="submit" class="btn-start">Get Started →</button>
    </form>
  </div>
<script>
if('serviceWorker' in navigator){navigator.serviceWorker.register('/sw.js').catch(()=>{});}
</script>
</body>
</html>
